ygData.messageBody:
Hiya
Welcome,
Most of us are around Freeport city. Recent events has seen us going to
HighHold pass , North Ro and the Oasis of Marr for adventuring .
But we will somehow be at FP for business and stuff.
Give us a "tell" when u r in. We will look out for u.

btw, "newbies should look out for a Singaporean wielding a Parang in a RED
dress, dangerous "creature"

Yiyang at HH pass
